== Issues ==
* The touchscreen works in `ts_test` but does not work in Weston or i3wm
* The Sym key does not work and gives no output in `xev`

On Android the {{Button|Alt}} key can be used to type symbols.

On pmOS this does not work (it only works as the Alt key), 
so currently there is currently no way of typing symbols.

Probably a custom keymap is needed

